Packages
net.varkhan.base.containers Enhanced Java data containers.

This package defines several abstract containers for Java data types, similar in purpose to the Java Collections framework, but with richer semantics.
net.varkhan.base.containers.array Optimized static methods operating on arrays or array-like data types.

This package groups into several classes static methods operating on Java arrays, or array-like operations on other data types.
net.varkhan.base.containers.list Indexed lists interfaces for various data types, and optimized implementations.

This package defines indexed lists, derived from the IndexedCollection interface, for generic object types and several specific data types.
